BTS spills the beans on Friends Reunion: We have shot for it but you’ll will have to wait to find out more

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / May 21, 2021, 12:02 (IST)

BTS has fans hooked to their latest number ‘Butter’ and during the launch of the song, the Bangtan Boys spilled a whole lot of secrets! Jin, Suga, J-Hope, RM, Jimin, V, and Jungkook will be a part of the highly-anticipated TV show ‘Friends: The Reunion’.

Controversial UK judge James Pickles dies at 85

Dec 23, 2010, 18:12 (IST)

James Pickles, an outspoken and controversial judge who didn't shy from insulting Britain's legal establishment, has died. He was 85.
